Titolo: Liberated (video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Liberated is a 2020 indie action-adventure video game developed by Polish studio Atomic Wolf and published by Walkabout Games. It was released worldwide on Nintendo Switch on June 2, 2020 with a version for Microsoft Windows on July 30, 2020.The game features hand-drawn interactive art in the style of a comic books, with the intent of making the player feel like they're inside an actual graphic novel. The story is a tech-noir/cyberpunk thriller about democracy slipping into authoritarianism.

Genere: action adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
